description:
Gorgo lives on the dark planet in the binary solar system. He is assigned to protect a Krotep Stone given to his tribe. Bogors are gigantic and very powerful. They use wild creatures they tamed in battles. Growing up on a planet that is dark almost all day, they can see very well at night.
Name : Gorgo
Tribe : Bogor
Planet :  Black Planet
Weapon of Choice: Sword
Religeon: Believes in sky god
